This directory redistributes the optimizer module
`src/optimizers/RiemannianLoRA.py` from the public repository
https://github.com/Bogachevv/RiemanianFinetune for the sole purpose of
reproducing the Riemannion (SGD, no momentum) baseline reported in this
paper.

At the time of this submission (May 2026), the upstream repository does not
include an explicit license file. Attribution is provided here in good
faith, the file is vendored unmodified, and no claim of authorship is made
over this third-party code. If you are the upstream author and wish this
copy to be removed or relicensed, please raise it through the submission
system.
